 al cuerpo.", "title_es": "Codos Abiertos", "description": "Elbows point out to the sides, stressing shoulder joints.", "description_es": "Los codos apuntan hacia los lados, estresando las articulaciones del hombro."}]', '["Knee Push-Ups: Modify by performing on your knees.", "Full Range: Go as low as comfortable, then push up fully.", "Breathing: Inhale as you lower, exhale as you push up."]', '["Flexiones de Rodillas: Modifica haciéndolas de rodillas.", "Rango Completo: Baja lo más cómodo, luego sube completamente.", "Respiración: Inhala al bajar, exhala al subir."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Push-Up%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
