0.0018600454,0.036002953,0.0050256434,0.0091640735,-0.038598742,-0.007471285,0.007914269,-0.018871056,0.005602753,0.0005318891,0.009101616,0.005182576,0.030673664]', 'Clean con Pesa Rusa', 'Empieza en bisagra de cadera, balancea la pesa rusa y redirígela a posición de rack a la altura del hombro en un movimiento fluido.', '["Start with kettlebell between feet, hinge at hips, chest up.", "Explode upwards, extending hips and knees, pull kettlebell close.", "As kettlebell rises, ''catch'' it in the rack position, elbow tucked.", "Stand tall, glutes squeezed. Lower with control to repeat."]', '["Inicia con la pesa rusa entre los pies, bisagra de cadera, pecho arriba.", "Explota hacia arriba, extiende caderas y rodillas, jala la pesa cerca.", "Mientras sube, ''atrapa'' la pesa en posición de rack, codo pegado.", "Ponte de pie, glúteos contraídos. Baja con control para repetir."]', '[{"avoid": "Maintain a neutral spine throughout the lift, engaging your core.", "title": "Rounding the Back", "avoid_es": "Mantén una columna neutra durante todo el levantamiento, activando tu core.", "title_es": "Redondear la Espalda", "description": "Lifting with a rounded back puts excessive strain on the lumbar spine, risking injury.", "description_es": "Levantar con la espalda redondeada ejerce una tensión excesiva en la columna lumbar, arriesgando lesiones."}, {"avoid": "Keep the elbow slightly bent and close to the body, absorbing the impact.", "title": "Catching with Straight Arm", "avoid_es": "Mantén el codo ligeramente flexionado y cerca del cuerpo, absorbiendo el impacto.", "title_es": "Atrapar con Brazo Recto", "description": "Catching the kettlebell with a straight arm can hyperextend the elbow or wrist.", "description_es": "Atrapar la pesa rusa con el brazo recto puede hiperextender el codo o la muñeca."}]', '[{"avoid": "Maintain a neutral spine throughout the lift, engaging your core.", "title": "Rounding the Back", "avoid_es": "Mantén una columna neutra durante todo el levantamiento, activando tu core.", "title_es": "Redondear la Espalda", "description": "Lifting with a rounded back puts excessive strain on the lumbar spine, risking injury.", "description_es": "Levantar con la espalda redondeada ejerce una tensión excesiva en la columna lumbar, arriesgando lesiones."}, {"avoid": "Keep the elbow slightly bent and close to the body, absorbing the impact.", "title": "Catching with Straight Arm", "avoid_es": "Mantén el codo ligeramente flexionado y cerca del cuerpo, absorbiendo el impacto.", "title_es": "Atrapar con Brazo Recto", "description": "Catching the kettlebell with a straight arm can hyperextend the elbow or wrist.", "description_es": "Atrapar la pesa rusa con el brazo recto puede hiperextender el codo o la muñeca."}]', '["Hip Drive: Initiate with a powerful hip thrust, not arm pull.", "Close Path: Keep the kettlebell close to your body during the pull.", "Rack Position: Elbow under the bell, wrist straight, bell resting."]', '["Impulso de Cadera: Inicia con un potente empuje de cadera, no con los brazos.", "Trayectoria Cercana: Mantén la pesa cerca de tu cuerpo al jalar.", "Posición de Rack: Codo bajo la pesa, muñeca recta, pesa apoyada."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Kettlebell%20Clean%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
