5224,0.027884223,-0.0057732374,-0.011599335,-0.034157526,0.012916523,0.003992754,-0.037162844,0.0048232772,0.021002293,0.015197139,-0.011140477,0.0044116634]', 'Caminata del Granjero', 'Sostén mancuernas o pesas rusas pesadas a los costados y camina durante una distancia o tiempo determinado, manteniendo postura erguida.', '["Grab heavy dumbbells or kettlebells, one in each hand, with an overhand grip.", "Stand tall, shoulders back, chest up, and core engaged. Look straight ahead.", "Walk slowly and deliberately for a set distance or time, maintaining posture.", "Keep your grip firm throughout the walk. Avoid swinging the weights."]', '["Sostén mancuernas o pesas rusas pesadas, una en cada mano, con agarre prono.", "Ponte de pie, hombros hacia atrás, pecho arriba y core activado. Mira al frente.", "Camina lenta y deliberadamente una distancia o tiempo, manteniendo la postura.", "Mantén el agarre firme durante la caminata. Evita balancear las pesas."]', '[{"avoid": "Maintain a tall, upright posture with shoulders pulled back and down.", "title": "Slouching Posture", "avoid_es": "Mantén una postura erguida con los hombros hacia atrás y abajo.", "title_es": "Postura Encorvada", "description": "Rounding your back and shoulders can strain your spine and reduce forearm engagement.", "description_es": "Encorvar la espalda y los hombros puede tensar la columna y reducir el trabajo del antebrazo."}, {"avoid": "Select weights that make your grip feel challenged from the start.", "title": "Using Too Light Weights", "avoid_es": "Selecciona pesas que hagan que tu agarre se sienta desafiado desde el principio.", "title_es": "Usar Pesas Demasiado Ligeras", "description": "If the weights are too light, your forearms won''t be sufficiently challenged for growth.", "description_es": "Si las pesas son muy ligeras, tus antebrazos no serán desafiados lo suficiente para crecer."}]', '[{"avoid": "Maintain a tall, upright posture with shoulders pulled back and down.", "title": "Slouching Posture", "avoid_es": "Mantén una postura erguida con los hombros hacia atrás y abajo.", "title_es": "Postura Encorvada", "description": "Rounding your back and shoulders can strain your spine and reduce forearm engagement.", "description_es": "Encorvar la espalda y los hombros puede tensar la columna y reducir el trabajo del antebrazo."}, {"avoid": "Select weights that make your grip feel challenged from the start.", "title": "Using Too Light Weights", "avoid_es": "Selecciona pesas que hagan que tu agarre se sienta desafiado desde el principio.", "title_es": "Usar Pesas Demasiado Ligeras", "description": "If the weights are too light, your forearms won''t be sufficiently challenged for growth.", "description_es": "Si las pesas son muy ligeras, tus antebrazos no serán desafiados lo suficiente para crecer."}]', '["Breathing: Breathe deeply and rhythmically throughout the walk.", "Grip Strength: Squeeze the weights as hard as possible.", "Core Engagement: Brace your core to stabilize your torso."]', '["Respiración: Respira profunda y rítmicamente durante la caminata.", "Fuerza de Agarre: Aprieta las pesas tan fuerte como sea posible.", "Core Activado: Contrae tu core para estabilizar el torso."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Farmer%20Walk%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
