9767182,0.0010117458,-0.001170755,0.012009036,-0.03916939,-7.48173e-05,0.005105316,-0.03775082,-0.0012911924,0.0068205968,0.012066422,0.01700243,0.000479023]', 'Rodillas Altas', 'Corre en el lugar llevando las rodillas a la altura de las caderas en cada zancada, bombeando los brazos al ritmo.', '["Stand tall, feet hip-width apart, gaze forward.", "Lift one knee towards your chest, opposite arm swings forward.", "Quickly switch, lifting the other knee, alternating arms.", "Maintain a light, quick pace, landing softly on the balls of your feet."]', '["Ponte de pie, pies al ancho de caderas, mira al frente.", "Levanta una rodilla hacia el pecho, el brazo opuesto se balancea hacia adelante.", "Cambia rápidamente, levantando la otra rodilla, alternando los brazos.", "Mantén un ritmo ligero y rápido, aterrizando suavemente sobre las puntas de los pies."]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your chest up and shoulders back throughout the exercise.", "title": "Slouching Posture", "avoid_es": "Mantén el pecho erguido y los hombros hacia atrás durante todo el ejercicio.", "title_es": "Postura Encorvada", "description": "Reduces core engagement and puts strain on the lower back.", "description_es": "Reduce la activación del core y ejerce tensión en la espalda baja."}, {"avoid": "Land softly on the balls of your feet, engaging your calves.", "title": "Landing Heavily", "avoid_es": "Aterriza suavemente sobre las puntas de los pies, activando las pantorrillas.", "title_es": "Aterrizaje Pesado", "description": "Increases impact on knees and ankles, leading to discomfort.", "description_es": "Aumenta el impacto en rodillas y tobillos, causando molestias."}]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your chest up and shoulders back throughout the exercise.", "title": "Slouching Posture", "avoid_es": "Mantén el pecho erguido y los hombros hacia atrás durante todo el ejercicio.", "title_es": "Postura Encorvada", "description": "Reduces core engagement and puts strain on the lower back.", "description_es": "Reduce la activación del core y ejerce tensión en la espalda baja."}, {"avoid": "Land softly on the balls of your feet, engaging your calves.", "title": "Landing Heavily", "avoid_es": "Aterriza suavemente sobre las puntas de los pies, activando las pantorrillas.", "title_es": "Aterrizaje Pesado", "description": "Increases impact on knees and ankles, leading to discomfort.", "description_es": "Aumenta el impacto en rodillas y tobillos, causando molestias."}]', '["Arm Drive: Use arms to help propel knees up.", "Core Tight: Engage abs to stabilize your torso.", "Breathe Rhythmically: Match breath to your movement."]', '["Impulso de Brazos: Usa brazos para impulsar rodillas.", "Core Firme: Activa abdominales para estabilizar.", "Respira Rítmicamente: Acompaña la respiración al movimiento."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=High%20Knees%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
