989797,-0.010507471,-0.019178964,0.007861601,-0.002620811,0.0056799212,-0.007091227,-0.036558874,-0.024276348,-0.0016726536,-0.046668548,0.0198166,0.022487536,-0.018714335,0.026871825,0.012344997]', 'Bicho Muerto', 'Recuéstate con brazos extendidos al techo y rodillas a 90 grados, baja el brazo y la pierna opuestos simultáneamente manteniendo la zona lumbar pegada al piso.', '["Lie on your back, arms extended towards the ceiling, knees bent at 90 degrees over hips.", "Engage your core, pressing your lower back into the floor.", "Slowly extend one arm and the opposite leg towards the floor without touching.", "Return to start, then repeat on the other side, maintaining core engagement."]', '["Acuéstate boca arriba, brazos extendidos al techo, rodillas flexionadas a 90 grados sobre caderas.", "Activa tu core, presionando la parte baja de tu espalda contra el suelo.", "Extiende lentamente un brazo y la pierna opuesta hacia el suelo sin tocar.", "Vuelve al inicio, luego repite en el otro lado, manteniendo el core activado."]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your lower back pressed into the floor throughout the movement.", "title": "Arching the Lower Back", "avoid_es": "Mantén la parte baja de tu espalda presionada contra el suelo durante todo el movimiento.", "title_es": "Arquear la Espalda Baja", "description": "Lifting the lower back off the floor reduces core engagement and can strain the spine.", "description_es": "Levantar la espalda baja del suelo reduce la activación del core y puede tensar la columna."}, {"avoid": "Perform each repetition slowly and with controlled movements.", "title": "Moving Too Fast", "avoid_es": "Realiza cada repetición lentamente y con movimientos controlados.", "title_es": "Moverse Demasiado Rápido", "description": "Rushing through the exercise compromises control and effectiveness, leading to poor form.", "description_es": "Apresurarse en el ejercicio compromete el control y la efectividad, llevando a una mala forma."}]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your lower back pressed into the floor throughout the movement.", "title": "Arching the Lower Back", "avoid_es": "Mantén la parte baja de tu espalda presionada contra el suelo durante todo el movimiento.", "title_es": "Arquear la Espalda Baja", "description": "Lifting the lower back off the floor reduces core engagement and can strain the spine.", "description_es": "Levantar la espalda baja del suelo reduce la activación del core y puede tensar la columna."}, {"avoid": "Perform each repetition slowly and with controlled movements.", "title": "Moving Too Fast", "avoid_es": "Realiza cada repetición lentamente y con movimientos controlados.", "title_es": "Moverse Demasiado Rápido", "description": "Rushing through the exercise compromises control and effectiveness, leading to poor form.", "description_es": "Apresurarse en el ejercicio compromete el control y la efectividad, llevando a una mala forma."}]', '["Breathing: Exhale as you extend, inhale as you return.", "Core Control: Imagine a string pulling your belly button to your spine.", "Head Position: Keep your neck neutral, gaze towards the ceiling."]', '["Respiración: Exhala al extender, inhala al volver.", "Control del Core: Imagina un hilo tirando de tu ombligo a la columna.", "Posición de la Cabeza: Mantén el cuello neutro, la mirada al techo."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Dead%20Bug%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
