le.", "title_es": "Arquear la espalda baja", "description": "Arching your lower back can strain the spine and reduce abdominal engagement.", "description_es": "Arquear la espalda baja puede tensar la columna y reducir la activación abdominal."}, {"avoid": "Perform the movement slowly and controlled, focusing on core strength.", "title": "Using Momentum", "avoid_es": "Realiza el movimiento de forma lenta y controlada, centrándote en la fuerza del core.", "title_es": "Usar el impulso", "description": "Relying on momentum rather than muscle control reduces exercise effectiveness.", "description_es": "Depender del impulso en lugar del control muscular reduce la efectividad del ejercicio."}]', '["Breathing: Exhale as you lift, inhale as you lower.", "Control: Avoid letting your limbs drop quickly.", "Focus: Keep your eyes on your feet during the lift."]', '["Respiración: Exhala al subir, inhala al bajar.", "Control: Evita que tus extremidades caigan rápido.", "Enfoque: Mantén la vista en tus pies al subir."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=V-Up%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
