8277,0.037864283,-0.003034832,-0.024086945,-0.025605038,-0.03651877,0.007876071,-0.008667891,-0.043624774,0.038435195,0.016958747,0.007071448,0.0078137955,0.009767918]', 'Curl de Muñeca Invertido con Barra', 'Sostén la barra con agarre prono, antebrazos sobre los muslos, y extiende las muñecas hacia arriba contra la resistencia para trabajar los extensores.', '["Sit, forearms on thighs, palms down, wrists off knees, holding barbell.", "Let barbell roll down to fingertips, extending wrists fully.", "Curl barbell up by flexing wrists, squeezing forearms at top.", "Slowly lower barbell back to starting position, controlling movement."]', '["Siéntate, antebrazos en muslos, palmas abajo, muñecas fuera de rodillas, sosteniendo barra.", "Deja que la barra ruede hasta las puntas de los dedos, extendiendo muñecas completamente.", "Sube la barra flexionando muñecas, apretando antebrazos arriba.", "Baja lentamente la barra a la posición inicial, controlando el movimiento."]', '[{"avoid": "Start with light weight, focusing on controlled movement and form.", "title": "Using too much weight", "avoid_es": "Empieza con poco peso, concéntrate en el movimiento controlado y la forma.", "title_es": "Usar demasiado peso", "description": "Heavy weight can strain wrist joints and tendons, leading to injury.", "description_es": "El peso excesivo puede tensar las articulaciones y tendones de la muñeca, causando lesiones."}, {"avoid": "Perform slow, controlled movements throughout the entire range of motion.", "title": "Jerking the weight", "avoid_es": "Realiza movimientos lentos y controlados en todo el rango de movimiento.", "title_es": "Mover el peso bruscamente", "description": "Using momentum instead of muscle reduces effectiveness and increases injury risk.", "description_es": "Usar el impulso en lugar del músculo reduce la efectividad y aumenta el riesgo de lesión."}]', '[{"avoid": "Start with light weight, focusing on controlled movement and form.", "title": "Using too much weight", 