72,0.007986076,0.0046310974,-0.0063413396,-0.029233716,0.008288355,-0.024193598,-0.017485019,0.010025581,-0.014630544,-0.011994922,0.012476682,-0.0020124358]', 'Remo en Cable Sentado', 'Siéntate en la máquina de remo con los pies en la plataforma, agarra el manubrio y hálalo hacia el abdomen inferior manteniendo el torso erguido.', '["Sit, feet on platform, knees slightly bent. Grab handle with overhand grip.", "Keep back straight, chest up. Pull handle towards lower abdomen.", "Squeeze shoulder blades together. Elbows close to body.", "Slowly extend arms, controlling the weight back to start."]', '["Siéntate, pies en plataforma, rodillas semiflexionadas. Agarra el asa con agarre prono.", "Mantén espalda recta, pecho erguido. Tira del asa hacia el abdomen bajo.", "Aprieta los omóplatos. Codos cerca del cuerpo.", "Extiende los brazos lentamente, controlando el peso de vuelta al inicio."]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your back straight and chest proud throughout the movement.", "title": "Rounding the Back", "avoid_es": "Mantén la espalda recta y el pecho erguido durante todo el movimiento.", "title_es": "Redondear la Espalda", "description": "Rounding your back, especially during the pull or release, can strain your lower spine.", "description_es": "Redondear la espalda, especialmente al tirar o soltar, puede tensar la columna lumbar."}, {"avoid": "Control the movement. Focus on a slow, deliberate pull and release.", "title": "Using Too Much Momentum", "avoid_es": "Controla el movimiento. Concéntrate en un tirón y una liberación lentos y deliberados.", "title_es": "Usar Demasiado Impulso", "description": "Jerking the weight with your body instead of pulling with your lats reduces muscle activation.", "description_es": "Tirar del peso con el cuerpo en lugar de con los dorsales reduce la activación muscular."}]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your back straight and chest proud throughout the movement.", "title": "Rounding the Back", "avoid_es": "Mantén la espalda recta y el pecho erguido durante todo el movimiento.", "title_es": "Redondear la Espalda", "description": "Rounding your back, especially during the pull or release, can strain your lower spine.", "description_es": "Redondear la espalda, especialmente al tirar o soltar, puede tensar la columna lumbar."}, {"avoid": "Control the movement. Focus on a slow, deliberate pull and release.", "title": "Using Too Much Momentum", "avoid_es": "Controla el movimiento. Concéntrate en un tirón y una liberación lentos y deliberados.", "title_es": "Usar Demasiado Impulso", "description": "Jerking the weight with your body instead of pulling with your lats reduces muscle activation.", "description_es": "Tirar del peso con el cuerpo en lugar de con los dorsales reduce la activación muscular."}]', '["Core Engagement: Brace your core to stabilize your torso.", "Shoulder Position: Keep shoulders down, away from ears.", "Breathing: Exhale as you pull, inhale as you release."]', '["Activación del Core: Contrae tu core para estabilizar el torso.", "Posición del Hombro: Mantén hombros abajo, lejos de las orejas.", "Respiración: Exhala al tirar, inhala al soltar."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Seated%20Cable%20Row%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
