9,0.018721431,0.015149579,0.013214062,0.015325642,0.009834353,-0.013858565,-0.00078627106,-0.023746382,0.020271206,0.019799171,-0.006945599,-0.010248686,0.016759524,0.0026646596,0.030254383,0.026570726]', 'Intervalos de Sprint', 'Corre a velocidad máxima durante una distancia o tiempo corto, descansa brevemente y repite; desarrolla potencia explosiva y capacidad cardiovascular simultáneamente.', '["Warm up with light cardio and dynamic stretches for 5-10 minutes.", "Sprint at maximum effort for 30 seconds.", "Recover with light jogging or walking for 60-90 seconds.", "Repeat sprint and recovery cycle 8-10 times. Cool down."]', '["Calienta con cardio ligero y estiramientos dinámicos durante 5-10 minutos.", "Corre a máxima intensidad durante 30 segundos.", "Recupérate trotando o caminando suavemente durante 60-90 segundos.", "Repite el ciclo de sprint y recuperación 8-10 veces. Enfría."]', '[{"avoid": "Always perform 5-10 minutes of light cardio and dynamic stretches.", "title": "Insufficient Warm-up", "avoid_es": "Realiza siempre 5-10 minutos de cardio ligero y estiramientos dinámicos.", "title_es": "Calentamiento Insuficiente", "description": "Skipping a proper warm-up can lead to muscle strains or pulls.", "description_es": "Saltarse un calentamiento adecuado puede provocar distensiones o tirones musculares."}, {"avoid": "Listen to your body; adjust sprint duration or recovery time as needed.", "title": "Overexertion", "avoid_es": "Escucha a tu cuerpo; ajusta la duración del sprint o el tiempo de recuperación.", "title_es": "Sobreexigencia", "description": "Pushing too hard without proper recovery can lead to injury or burnout.", "description_es": "Esforzarse demasiado sin una recuperación adecuada puede causar lesiones o agotamiento."}]', '[{"avoid": "Always perform 5-10 minutes of light cardio and dynamic stretches.", "title": "Insufficient Warm-up", "avoid_es": "Realiza siempre 5-10 minutos de cardio ligero y estiramientos dinámicos.", "title_es": "Calentamiento Insuficiente", "description": "Skipping a proper warm-up can lead to muscle strains or pulls.", "description_es": "Saltarse un calentamiento adecuado puede provocar distensiones o tirones musculares."}, {"avoid": "Listen to your body; adjust sprint duration or recovery time as needed.", "title": "Overexertion", "avoid_es": "Escucha a tu cuerpo; ajusta la duración del sprint o el tiempo de recuperación.", "title_es": "Sobreexigencia", "description": "Pushing too hard without proper recovery can lead to injury or burnout.", "description_es": "Esforzarse demasiado sin una recuperación adecuada puede causar lesiones o agotamiento."}]', '["Form Focus: Maintain an upright posture and engage your core.", "Breathing Control: Use deep, controlled breaths during recovery.", "Progressive Overload: Gradually increase sprint duration or reps."]', '["Enfoque en la forma: Mantén una postura erguida y activa tu core.", "Control de la respiración: Usa respiraciones profundas y controladas.", "Sobrecarga progresiva: Aumenta gradualmente la duración o las repeticiones."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Sprint%20Intervals%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
