6,0.0032844646,-0.004982078,0.00018121123,-0.006285644,0.0017627152,-0.0060582436,-0.03984919,-0.0074074417,0.014793317,-0.00672728,0.047653727,0.017558701]', 'Abdominal', 'Recuéstate con rodillas flexionadas, coloca las manos detrás de la cabeza y flexiona la columna para despegar los omóplatos del piso apretando los abdominales.', '["Lie on your back, knees bent, feet flat on the floor, hands behind your head.", "Engage your abs, lift your head and shoulders off the floor.", "Keep your lower back pressed into the floor. Exhale as you lift.", "Slowly lower back down to the starting position. Inhale as you lower."]', '["Acuéstate boca arriba, rodillas flexionadas, pies apoyados, manos detrás de la cabeza.", "Contrae los abdominales, levanta la cabeza y los hombros del suelo.", "Mantén la zona lumbar pegada al suelo. Exhala al subir.", "Baja lentamente a la posición inicial. Inhala al bajar."]', '[{"avoid": "Support your head gently; focus on ab contraction, not neck pulling.", "title": "Neck Strain", "avoid_es": "Sostén la cabeza suavemente; concéntrate en la contracción abdominal, no en tirar del cuello.", "title_es": "Tensión en el Cuello", "description": "Pulling on your neck instead of engaging your abs can cause strain.", "description_es": "Tirar del cuello en lugar de contraer los abdominales puede causar tensión."}, {"avoid": "Keep your lower back pressed into the floor throughout the movement.", "title": "Lower Back Arching", "avoid_es": "Mantén la zona lumbar pegada al suelo durante todo el movimiento.", "title_es": "Arqueo Lumbar", "description": "Lifting too high or too fast can cause your lower back to arch, leading to discomfort.", "description_es": "Levantar demasiado alto o rápido puede arquear la espalda baja, causando molestias."}]', '[{"avoid": "Support your head gently; focus on ab contraction, not neck pulling.", "title": "Neck Strain", "avoid_es": "Sostén la cabeza suavemente; concéntrate en la contracción abdominal, no en tirar del cuello.", "title_es": "Tensión en el Cuello", "description": "Pulling on your neck instead of engaging your abs can cause strain.", "description_es": "Tirar del cuello en lugar de contraer los abdominales puede causar tensión."}, {"avoid": "Keep your lower back pressed into the floor throughout the movement.", "title": "Lower Back Arching", "avoid_es": "Mantén la zona lumbar pegada al suelo durante todo el movimiento.", "title_es": "Arqueo Lumbar", "description": "Lifting too high or too fast can cause your lower back to arch, leading to discomfort.", "description_es": "Levantar demasiado alto o rápido puede arquear la espalda baja, causando molestias."}]', '["Breathing: Exhale on the effort (up), inhale on the release (down).", "Mind-Muscle: Focus on feeling your abs contract, not just moving.", "Controlled Movement: Avoid momentum; use slow, deliberate motions."]', '["Respiración: Exhala al subir, inhala al bajar.", "Conexión: Siente la contracción abdominal, no solo el movimiento.", "Movimiento Controlado: Evita el impulso; movimientos lentos y deliberados."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Crunch%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
