,0.0021600684,0.016191278,-0.0014109795,-0.0031000373,0.009962962,-0.03349565,-0.04707329,0.00035789362,0.007966607,-0.021677097,-0.016036723,0.0056379396,0.004000412,0.03304725,-0.012585883]', 'Dominada con Agarre Neutro', 'Cuélgate de manijas paralelas con agarre neutro (palmas enfrentadas) y sube el mentón por encima del nivel de las manos, enfatizando los dorsales inferiores y bíceps.', '["Grab parallel bars with a neutral grip, hands shoulder-width apart.", "Hang with arms fully extended, engaging your core.", "Pull yourself up until your chin clears the bar, squeezing your lats.", "Lower yourself slowly and with control to the starting position."]', '["Sujeta barras paralelas con agarre neutro, manos al ancho de hombros.", "Cuélgate con brazos extendidos, activando tu core.", "Sube hasta que tu barbilla pase la barra, contrayendo tus dorsales.", "Baja lenta y controladamente a la posición inicial."]', '[{"avoid": "Ensure full extension at the bottom and chin above the bar at the top.", "title": "Incomplete Range of Motion", "avoid_es": "Asegura extensión completa abajo y barbilla sobre la barra arriba.", "title_es": "Rango de Movimiento Incompleto", "description": "Not fully extending at the bottom or not pulling high enough reduces muscle activation.", "description_es": "No extender completamente abajo o no subir lo suficiente reduce la activación muscular."}, {"avoid": "Perform each rep with controlled movement, focusing on muscle contraction.", "title": "Using Momentum", "avoid_es": "Realiza cada repetición con movimiento controlado, enfocándote en la contracción muscular.", "title_es": "Usar Impulso", "description": "Kipping or swinging to complete reps reduces lat engagement and increases injury risk.", "description_es": "Hacer ''kipping'' o balancearse para completar repeticiones reduce el trabajo de los dorsales y aumenta el riesgo de lesión."}]', '[{"avoid": "Ensure full extension at the bottom and chin above the bar at the top.", "title": "Incomplete Range of Motion", "avoid_es": "Asegura extensión completa abajo y barbilla sobre la barra arriba.", "title_es": "Rango de Movimiento Incompleto", "description": "Not fully extending at the bottom or not pulling high enough reduces muscle activation.", "description_es": "No extender completamente abajo o no subir lo suficiente reduce la activación muscular."}, {"avoid": "Perform each rep with controlled movement, focusing on muscle contraction.", "title": "Using Momentum", "avoid_es": "Realiza cada repetición con movimiento controlado, enfocándote en la contracción muscular.", "title_es": "Usar Impulso", "description": "Kipping or swinging to complete reps reduces lat engagement and increases injury risk.", "description_es": "Hacer ''kipping'' o balancearse para completar repeticiones reduce el trabajo de los dorsales y aumenta el riesgo de lesión."}]', '["Scapular Retraction: Initiate pull by retracting shoulder blades.", "Elbows Down: Focus on driving elbows towards your hips.", "Controlled Descent: Lower slowly to maximize time under tension."]', '["Retracción Escapular: Inicia el jalón retrayendo las escápulas.", "Codos Abajo: Concéntrate en llevar los codos hacia tus caderas.", "Descenso Controlado: Baja lentamente para maximizar el tiempo bajo tensión."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Neutral-Grip%20Pull-Up%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
