4040374,0.004621442,0.0030547748,-0.028690903,-0.020901427,0.0015434866,-0.053283915,-0.007506725,0.019948227,0.00050136115,0.0176536,0.013858551]', 'Elevación de Rodillas Colgado', 'Cuélgate de una barra, tensa el core y eleva ambas rodillas hacia el pecho, luego baja con control.', '["Hang from a bar with an overhand grip, hands shoulder-width apart.", "Engage your core and lift your knees towards your chest.", "Pause briefly at the top, squeezing your abdominal muscles.", "Slowly lower your legs back to the starting position with control."]', '["Cuelga de una barra con agarre prono, manos al ancho de los hombros.", "Activa tu core y levanta las rodillas hacia el pecho.", "Haz una breve pausa arriba, contrayendo los músculos abdominales.", "Baja lentamente las piernas a la posición inicial con control."]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your body still; focus on controlled leg lifts using only your abs.", "title": "Swinging Body", "avoid_es": "Mantén el cuerpo quieto; concéntrate en levantar las piernas solo con los abdominales.", "title_es": "Balanceo del Cuerpo", "description": "Using momentum from swinging reduces core engagement and can strain the lower back.", "description_es": "Usar el impulso del balanceo reduce la activación del core y puede tensar la espalda baja."}, {"avoid": "Aim to bring your knees above your hips or as close to your chest as possible.", "title": "Incomplete Range of Motion", "avoid_es": "Intenta llevar las rodillas por encima de las caderas o lo más cerca posible del pecho.", "title_es": "Rango de Movimiento Incompleto", "description": "Not lifting knees high enough limits abdominal contraction and effectiveness.", "description_es": "No levantar las rodillas lo suficiente limita la contracción abdominal y la efectividad."}]', '[{"avoid": "Keep your body still; focus on controlled leg lifts using only your abs.", "title": "Swinging Body", "avoid_es": "Mantén el cuerpo quieto; concéntrate en levantar las piernas solo con los abdominales.", "title_es": "Balanceo del Cuerpo", "description": "Using momentum from swinging reduces core engagement and can strain the lower back.", "description_es": "Usar el impulso del balanceo reduce la activación del core y puede tensar la espalda baja."}, {"avoid": "Aim to bring your knees above your hips or as close to your chest as possible.", "title": "Incomplete Range of Motion", "avoid_es": "Intenta llevar las rodillas por encima de las caderas o lo más cerca posible del pecho.", "title_es": "Rango de Movimiento Incompleto", "description": "Not lifting knees high enough limits abdominal contraction and effectiveness.", "description_es": "No levantar las rodillas lo suficiente limita la contracción abdominal y la efectividad."}]', '["Breathing: Exhale as you lift your knees, inhale as you lower them.", "Core Engagement: Imagine pulling your belly button towards your spine.", "Controlled Descent: Avoid letting gravity drop your legs quickly."]', '["Respiración: Exhala al subir las rodillas, inhala al bajarlas.", "Activación del Core: Imagina tirar del ombligo hacia la columna.", "Descenso Controlado: Evita que la gravedad baje tus piernas rápido."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Hanging%20Knee%20Raise%20proper%20form%20tutorial'),
