3,0.023522086,0.007795978,-0.03798428,-0.0050731143,0.0036679853,0.009067869,0.019891834,0.0084640505]', 'Press de Hombros en Máquina', 'Siéntate en la máquina de press de hombros, agarra los manubrios a la altura de los hombros y empuja hacia arriba hasta extensión completa del codo.', '["Adjust seat height so handles are at shoulder level. Sit with back flat against pad.", "Grasp handles with an overhand grip, palms facing forward. Elbows slightly in front of body.", "Press handles upward until arms are almost fully extended, but do not lock elbows.", "Slowly lower the handles back to the starting position, maintaining control."]', '["Ajusta el asiento para que las asas estén a la altura de los hombros. Siéntate con la espalda plana.", "Agarra las asas con un agarre por encima, palmas hacia adelante. Codos ligeramente delante.", "Empuja las asas hacia arriba hasta que los brazos estén casi extendidos, sin bloquear codos.", "Baja lentamente las asas a la posición inicial, manteniendo el control."]', '[{"avoid": "Stop just short of full elbow extension. Keep a slight bend in your elbows.", "title": "Locking Elbows", "avoid_es": "Detente justo antes de la extensión completa del codo. Mantén una ligera flexión.", "title_es": "Bloquear los Codos", "description": "Fully extending and locking your elbows at the top of the movement can put undue stress on the elbow joints.", "description_es": "Extender y bloquear completamente los codos en la parte superior del movimiento puede ejercer una tensión indebida en las articulaciones del codo."}, {"avoid": "Start with a lighter weight to master the form. Gradually increase as strength improves.", "title": "Using Too Much Weight", "avoid_es": "Comienza con un peso ligero para dominar la forma. Aumenta gradualmente.", "title_es": "Usar Demasiado Peso", "description": "Lifting a weight that is too heavy can compromise form, leading to injury or reduced effectiveness.", "description_es": "Levantar un peso excesivo puede comprometer la forma, provocando lesiones o menor efectividad."}]', '[{"avoid": "Stop just short of full elbow extension. Keep a slight bend in your elbows.", "title": "Locking Elbows", "avoid_es": "Detente justo antes de la extensión completa del codo. Mantén una ligera flexión.", "title_es": "Bloquear los Codos", "description": "Fully extending and locking your elbows at the top of the movement can put undue stress on the elbow joints.", "description_es": "Extender y bloquear completamente los codos en la parte superior del movimiento puede ejercer una tensión indebida en las articulaciones del codo."}, {"avoid": "Start with a lighter weight to master the form. Gradually increase as strength improves.", "title": "Using Too Much Weight", "avoid_es": "Comienza con un peso ligero para dominar la forma. Aumenta gradualmente.", "title_es": "Usar Demasiado Peso", "description": "Lifting a weight that is too heavy can compromise form, leading to injury or reduced effectiveness.", "description_es": "Levantar un peso excesivo puede comprometer la forma, provocando lesiones o menor efectividad."}]', '["Control the Movement: Avoid using momentum; focus on slow, controlled lifts.", "Maintain Posture: Keep your back firmly against the pad throughout the exercise.", "Breathing: Exhale as you press up, inhale as you lower the weight."]', '["Controla el Movimiento: Evita el impulso; concéntrate en levantamientos lentos.", "Mantén la Postura: Mantén la espalda firme contra el respaldo durante el ejercicio.", "Respiración: Exhala al subir, inhala al bajar el peso."]', 'https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Machine%20Shoulder%20Press%20proper%20form%20tutorial');
